The file is a single-row-group Parquet written by Arrow with Snappy-compressed dictionary pages and RLE-dictionary data pages. I have enough footer structure now; I’m decoding the page bodies so row-level regressions can be run locally.
exec
"C:\\WINDOWS\\System32\\WindowsPowerShell\\v1.0\\powershell.exe" -Command "@'
